  <original-body>ActionController::Base#redirect_to doesn't handle complex URI schemes (per http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/URI_scheme).  This means that URL handlers such as &quot;x-iphone-app&quot; can't be redirected to by Rails apps.

redirect_to patch:
http://github.com/mojodna/rails/commit/677a6bc41142c0561ea8e331aada1c351191ec29

corresponding test:
http://github.com/mojodna/rails/commit/bff6d6ea1faad83a1df5e984fbd1bc0092f74237</original-body>
